com.example.meditrackr.models.record

Class PhotoList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.meditrackr.models.record.PhotoList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PhotoList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    PhotoList: A list of photos (Bitmap objects) for a record. Allows adding and removing elements (by both index and bitmap), checking if a Bitmap object exists in the array and retrieving the size of the list.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
